OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FFor #30 cash, I leave with a pink
OL,8,Fnasal spray. There is no label, no
OL,9,Fingredients list and zero instructions.
OL,11,FSo what's actually in it?
OL,13,FThese sprays typically contain
OL,14,FMelanotan 2, a synthetic hormone that
OL,15,Fdarkens skin pigmentation, but it's
OL,16,Fnot authorised, licensed, or regulated
OL,17,Ffor use in the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAt the next salon I manage to buy
OL,8,Fanother nasal spray, this time for
OL,9,F#20, but when I question the seller
OL,10,Fabout what's actually inside it, she
OL,11,Fsays: "I haven't got a clue!"
OL,13,FBut it's the last stop that really
OL,14,Fshocks me: Euphoria Tanning in Cwmbran.
OL,26,@sD@GOUsD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
