OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FI step into the nightclub-like shop
OL,8,Fwhere I am offered both nasal sprays
OL,9,Fand tanning injections. Despite having
OL,10,Ffaced warnings and fines for past
OL,11,Fwrongdoings, here they are once again,
OL,12,Fwilling to sell potentially dangerous
OL,13,Finjectables to anyone chasing a quick
OL,14,Ftan.
OL,16,FThe seller shows me two different
OL,17,Fvials for injection: "This is it
OL,18,Fmixed, this is it unmixed."
OL,26,@yD@VOUzD@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
