OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FMixed with what? In what dosage?
OL,8,FWhere? By whom? I'm full of questions
OL,9,Fbut the seller quickly reassures me.
OL,10,FAs for the risks? They reply:
OL,11,F"Literally nothing, the only thing is
OL,12,Fyou'll be tanned."
OL,14,FExperts disagree and warn of serious
OL,15,Fpotential health risks, including
OL,16,Fkidney damage and an increased risk of
OL,17,Fskin cancer.
OL,19,FI tried to contact all three salons
OL,20,Fnumerous times for a comment but none
OL,21,Fof them responded.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
