OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FI showed my undercover footage to Dr.
OL,8,FMegan Samuel, a maxillofacial surgeon
OL,9,Fwho also specialises in aesthetics.
OL,11,F"Shocking", "worrying", "crazy" - are
OL,12,Fjust some of her reactions.
OL,14,FShe said: "It makes me angry watching
OL,15,Fthis because I feel like there are
OL,16,Fvulnerable people in society that want
OL,17,Fto make themselves feel better and
OL,18,Fthey go to these places and these are
OL,19,Fthe people who they're greeted with,
OL,20,Fwho just want to make a quick sale."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]sD@MOUsD@VO]sD@YOUsD@_O]vD@
OL,26,AKOU|D@dO]
