FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FIn regards to the injectables
OL,8,Fcontaining Melanotan 2, the MHRA, the
OL,9,Fauthority that regulates medicines in
OL,10,Fthe UK, said that these products "meet
OL,11,Fthe definition of a medicinal product"
OL,12,Fbut they are "not authorised for use
OL,13,Fin the UK".
OL,15,FThey added: "Products determined as
OL,16,Fmedicines which do not hold the
OL,17,Frequired authorisations are in breach
OL,18,Fof Human Medicines Regulations 2012
OL,19,F(HMRs) and appropriate regulatory
OL,20,Faction will be taken to remove these
OL,21,Fproducts from sale."
OL,26,@rD@bOUsD@fO]tD@NOUwD@MOU}D@TO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
