FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781039474
OL,3,CUndercover investigation into
OL,4,Cunlicensed tanning products sold in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAs for the nasal sprays, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for the Department for
OL,9,FBusiness and Trade said that "anyone
OL,10,Fselling nasal tanning sprays,
OL,11,Fincluding online, must ensure they are
OL,12,Fsafe before placing them on the
OL,13,Fmarket".
OL,26,@qD@^OU
